Title: Shipping Wars
Actors: Marc Springer, Roy Garber, Jennifer Brennan, Bill Lloyd, Chris Kikelhan, Christopher Hanna, Dusty Davie, Jarrett Joyce, Jessica Samko, Johnny Chavez, Robbie Welsh, Tamera Sturgis, Todd Sturgis
Plot: Show revolves around teams of independent heavy-duty moving companies bidding for the chance to transport unshipable items, from oversized loads to bulky packages and bizarre items.
